---
// Footer component
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-neutral-900 text-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 md:gap-12">
      <!-- Brand -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-white rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="1.5" fill="#3B82F6"/>
              <circle cx="20" cy="12" r="1.5" fill="#3B82F6"/>
              <path d="M11 18c1.5 2 3.5 2 5 2s3.5 0 5-2" stroke="#3B82F6" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <rect x="10" y="22" width="12" height="3" rx="1.5" fill="#3B82F6" fill-opacity="0.9"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-xl font-bold">Keep Aligned</span>
        </a>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 max-w-sm">
          La app que te ayuda a mantener tu tratamiento de ortodoncia invisible bajo control. 
          Seguí tu progreso, registrá tus horas y alcanzá la sonrisa que querés.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Links -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-semibold mb-4">Enlaces</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li>
            <a href="#features" class="text-neutral-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Funciones</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="#app" class="text-neutral-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">La App</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="#orthodontists" class="text-neutral-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Ortodoncistas</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Legal -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-semibold mb-4">Legal</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li>
            <a href="/privacy" class="text-neutral-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Privacidad</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom bar -->
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-neutral-800 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
      <div class="text-center md:text-left">
        <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm mb-2 md:mb-0">
          © {currentYear} Keep Aligned. Todos los derechos reservados.
        </p>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 text-xs">
          Designed & Built by 
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/agustinarone/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-neutral-400 transition-colors">Agustín Arone</a> 
          & 
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/juancruz-mancusomicka/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-neutral-400 transition-colors">Juan Mancuso</a>
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Store badges small -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <a href="https://apps.apple.com/ar/app/keep-aligned/id6755775658" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
          <img src="https://developer.apple.com/assets/elements/badges/download-on-the-app-store.svg" alt="Download on App Store" class="h-8" />
        </a>
        <div class="opacity-30 cursor-not-allowed">
          <img src="https://play.google.com/intl/en_us/badges/static/images/badges/en_badge_web_generic.png" alt="Get it on Google Play" class="h-12 -my-2" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

